squo;re involved in disciplinary action </li>\n  <li>you haven&rsquo;t done any testing for some time</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>When you&rsquo;re due to take the refresher course you&rsquo;ll be sent a message via  the MOT computer system at your test station.</p>\n\n<p>The first message will be issued when your training is due in 180 days,  followed by a second message 30 days later.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>If you don’t take the refresher course you’ll be sent a final message  saying your training is overdue - you’ll be suspended from testing until  you complete the course.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Booking your course</h2>\n\n<p>You can book either:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>through the MOT computer system</li>\n  <li>by filling out form VT76</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dft.gov.uk/vosa/repository/VT76%20Form%20Jul%2012.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Form VT76 - Nominated Tester Training - existing testers application' (PDF, 243KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Form VT76 - Nominated Tester Training - existing testers application’ (PDF, 243KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Return your form to <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\n<abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> Training Services   \n<br /> Booking Section  \n<br /> Berkeley House  \n<br /> Croydon Street  \n<br /> Bristol BS5 0DA\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n"}]},"updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:26:18+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Driving and transport businesses","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving%2Fbusinesses.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes setting up test stations, employing drivers and becoming a vehicle operator","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fbusinesses","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/businesses"},"parent":{"title":"Driving, transport, and travel","id":"