 when you&rsquo;re ready and they&rsquo;ll arrange a visit.</p>\n\n<p>If it fails the inspection, you’ll be told what needs to be done and given a deadline to send in new plans.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>If your site fails its final inspection, <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> will send you a letter telling you what you need to do.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Approval</h2>\n\n<p>When <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> has given final approval, you’ll get your certificate and can operate as an <abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr>. You&rsquo;ll have to operate under the terms set out in the <abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr> contract.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.transportoffice.gov.uk/crt/repository/ATF%20Contract.pdf\" title=\"Download 'ATF contract (PDF, 302KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr> contract’ (PDF, 302KB)</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://www.transportoffice.gov.uk/crt/repository/atf%20explanatory%20notes%20.pdf\" title=\"Download ‘ATF contract - explanatory notes’ (PDF, 44KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr> contract - explanatory notes’ (PDF, 44KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/setting-up-an-authorised-testing-facility/operating-your-atf","slug":"operating-your-atf","order":5,"title":"Operating your ATF","body":"<p>Once you&rsquo;ve been approved to operate an Authorised Testing Facility (<abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr>), there are certain things you must do.</p>\n\n<h2>Set up a pre-funded account (<abbr title=\"pre-funded account\">PFA</abbr>)</h2>\n\n<p>If you already have a <abbr title=\"pre-funded account\">PFA</abbr>, you can use this for your <abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr>. If you don&rsquo;t, you&rsquo;ll need to set one up. </p>\n\n<p>With a <abbr title=\"pre-funded account\">PFA</abbr> you’ll be able to access the Vehicle and Operator Services Agency&rsquo;s (<abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>’s) goods and services whenever you need them.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You need a separate <abbr title=\"pre-funded account\">PFA</abbr> for each <abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr> site.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.transportoffice.gov.uk/crt/repository/ATF%20pre%20funded%20account.pdf\" title=\"Download ‘ATF pre-funded account guidance and application form’ (PDF, 45KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr> pre-funded account guidance and application form’ (PDF, 45KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Meet health and safety requirements</h2>\n\n<p>You must ensure your premises meet health and safety regulations. During site visits <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> may ask to see any relevant documents, eg public liability insurance certificate, fire risk assessment etc.</p>\n\n<h2>Display logos and signage</h2>\n\n<p>You must display at least one <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr> logo even if you only service your own vehicles. </p>\n\n<p>If you offer third party or open access testing the logo should be displayed as explained in\nthe brand guidelines.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.transportoffice.gov.uk/crt/repository/ATF%20Brand%20Identity%20Guidelines.pdf\" title=\"Download VOSA’s ATF brand guidelines’ (PDF, 1.56MB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>’s <abbr title=\"Authorised Testing Facility\">ATF</abbr> brand guidelines’ (PDF, 1.56MB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>It’s your responsibilit