<p>The <abbr title=\"Authorised Examiner\">AE</abbr> is responsible for making sure that:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the test facilities and equipment are checked and well-maintained </li>\n  <li>the <a href=\"/become-an-mot-tester\" title=\"become an MOT tester\">Nominated Testers</a> are assessed correctly and complete training and quality checks</li>\n  <li><abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> staff have access to the premises for checks on staff and equipment</li>\n  <li>MOT documents are correctly stored and access to electronic MOT test systems is only given to eligible users</li>\n  <li>MOT tests are properly conducted</li>\n  <li><abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> is informed about significant changes to the business within 7 working days</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>There&rsquo;s more information about the <abbr title=\"Authorised Examiner\">AE</abbr>&rsquo;s responsibilities in <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>&rsquo;s guide to becoming an <abbr title=\"Authorised Examiner\">AE</abbr>. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/Transport_Theme_files/So_you_want_to_be_an_Authorised_Examiner.pdf\" title=\"Download 'So you want to become an Authorised Examiner?' (PDF, 361KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘So you want to become an Authorised Examiner?’ (PDF, 361KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>To apply for <abbr title=\"Authorised Examiner\">AE</abbr> status, send form VT01 to <abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>. Use the same form if you already have <abbr title=\"Authorised Examiner\">AE</abbr> status and want to open a test station. The guide to requirements for authorisation of <abbr title=\"Authorised Examiners\">AEs</abbr> tells you more about the application process.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/Transport_Theme_files/Application_for_MOT_Authorisation_VT01_1110.pdf\" title=\"