</abbr>) monitors the standard of instruction given by:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>approved training bodies (<abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATBs</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>instructors delivering compulsory basic training (<abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr>) courses</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You must make your instructors available for regular quality  assurance assessments. </p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You should tell your local <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> <abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr> manager the dates and times when your <abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr> will be running <abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr> courses.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>After an assessment</h2>\n\n<p>You&rsquo;ll get a letter of confirmation and report from <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> after an assessment visit if the training delivered meets the required standard.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> can conduct more assessments if:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the training falls short of the required standard</li>\n  <li>there are breaches of regulations</li>\n  <li>there are reports of failure to follow the conditions of appointment</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> will consider withdrawing an instructor&rsquo;s authority to deliver courses if they fail to achieve the required standard during the subsequent assessments. </p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> can withdraw your <abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr>’s authorisation to deliver training courses if assessments show that it doesn’t consistently provide full and proper <abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr> courses.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Disagreeing with <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>&rsquo;s decision</h2>\n\n<p>You can appeal to <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> if you or an instructor disagrees with <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>&rsquo;s decision to withdraw their authority.</p>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\n\n<br />Chief Driving Examiner\n<br />Driving Standards Agency\n<br />The Axis Building\n<br />112 Upper Parliament Street\n<br />Nottingham\n<br />NG1 6LP\n<br />\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/set-up-run-motorcycle-approved-training-body-atb/documents-for-atbs","slug":"documents-for-atbs","order":7,"title":"Documents for ATBs","body":"<p>The Driving Standards Agency produces the following documents for approved training bodies (<abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATBs</abbr>).</p>\n\n<h2><abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr> manual</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr> manual gives more details about the rules and processes you should follow when you&rsquo;re running an <abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://assets.dft.gov.uk/dsa-bl/dsa-atb-manual.pdf\" title=\"Download 'ATB manual' (PDF, 190KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Approved training body\">ATB</abbr> manual’ (PDF, 190KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Safe and Responsible Riding (Category A/P) Standard</h2>\n\n<p>The &lsquo;Safe and Responsible Riding (Category A/P) Standard&rsquo; sets out the skills, knowledge and understanding that learners will need to prove to be safe and responsible rider.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/dsa-national-driving-riding-standards/dsa-riding-standard.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Safe and Responsible Riding (Category A/P) Standard' (PDF, 207KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Safe and Responsible Riding (Category A/P) Standard’ (PDF, 207KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Compulsory basic training (<abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr>) syllabus and guidance notes</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr> syllabus and guidance notes sets out what trainers need to do and what learners need to understand when taking the course. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/dsa-national-driving-riding-standards/dsa-cbt-syllabus-guidance-notes.pdf\" title=\"Download 'CBT syllabus and guidance notes' (PDF, 115KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr> syllabus and guidance notes’ (PDF, 115KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Direct access scheme (<abbr title=\"Direct access scheme\">DAS</abbr>) motorcycle training guidance</h2>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Direct access scheme\">DAS</abbr> motorcycle training guidance sets out what trainers need to do and what learners need to understand when taking the course. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://assets.dft.gov.uk/publications/dsa-national-driving-riding-standards/dsa-direct-access-scheme-das-guidance-notes.pdf\" title=\"Download 'DAS motorcycle training guidance' (PDF, 109KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘<abbr title=\"Direct access scheme\">DAS</abbr> motorcycle training guidance’ (PDF, 109KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"}]},"updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:26:14+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Teaching people to drive","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Becoming an instructor, applying for licences, booking tests and rules","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/teaching-people-to-drive"},"parent":{"title":"Driving, transport, and travel","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrappin