ion applicants on how conditions added to the licence may affect their business</li>\n  <li>ask applicants and objectors to sum up their cases</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The traffic commissioner will announce their <a href=\"/traffic-commissioner/decision-and-penalties\" title=\"Find out more about the decisions a commissioner can make\">decision</a> at the time, or give it in writing later, usually within 28 days.</p>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/traffic-commissioner/decision-and-penalties","slug":"decision-and-penalties","order":5,"title":"Decision and penalties","body":"<p>The traffic commissioner can decide to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>refuse to grant a licence </li>\n  <li>refuse to vary an existing licence </li>\n  <li>attach conditions to a licence </li>\n  <li>grant a licence allowing fewer vehicles than the number applied for </li>\n  <li>impose financial penalties on registered bus service operators</li>\n  <li>end or suspend an existing licence </li>\n  <li>disqualify an individual or a company from having a licence</li>\n  <li>disqualify transport managers</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You can <a href=\"/traffic-commissioner/appeals\" title=\"Find out about making an appeal\">appeal</a> the decision.</p>\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/traffic-commissioner/appeals","slug":"appeals","order":6,"title":"Appeals","body":"<p>You can appeal against a decision by the traffic commissioner to the Upper Tribunal Administrative Appeals Chamber. </p>\n\n<p>You need to complete Form UT12, &lsquo;Notice of Appeal against a decision of a traffic commissioner&rsquo;. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/forms/tribunals/aa/UT12_TC_Appealform.pdf\" title=\"Form UT12\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘UT12 ‘Notice of Appeal against a decision of a traffic commissioner’ (PDF, 152KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You must send the form to the chamber within 1 month of the traffic commissioner&rsquo;s written decision. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<p>