br title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr></li>\n  <li>you&rsquo;ll have to pay <abbr title=\"Value Added Tax\">VAT</abbr> on the fee</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Cost of the schemes</h2>\n\n<p>You have to <a href=\"/vehicle-approval/inspection-fees\" title=\"Inspection fees\">pay a fee</a> for the Vehicle and Operator Services Agency (<abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr>) to inspect your vehicle. </p>\n\n<h2>How to apply</h2>\n\n<p>To get Voluntary <abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr> for a passenger car or light goods vehicle (up to 3,500 kg), send a completed application to the address on the form. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/Transport_files/Application_for_VIVA_M1_N1_1.doc\" title=\"Download 'Application for Voluntary Individual Vehicle Approval' (DOC, 709KB)\">Download ‘Application for Voluntary Individual Vehicle Approval’ (DOC, 709KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> has produced guidance on completing the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.businesslink.gov.uk/Transport_files/VIVA_M1_N1_Guidance_Notes.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Guidance on completing Voluntary Individual Vehicle Approval application form' (PDF, 60KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Guidance on completing Voluntary Individual Vehicle Approval application form’ (PDF, 60KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Voluntary <abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr> applications for larger passenger cars, goods vehicles and trailers can be made on the Statutory <abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr> form.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>What happens next?</h2>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Vehicle and Operator Services Agency\">VOSA</abbr> will carry out an inspection of the vehicle. If it passes, you&rsquo;ll be given a &lsquo;Confirmation of Compliance&rsquo; notification (not an ap